    "body": "Is there any plan to implement this feature?\r\nHaving few production contracts an a lot of surrounding  test contracts is a common practice.\r\nCurrent (single-compiler settings) require either very slow project compilation, since all tests (and unused library contracts) are required to be optimized, or testing the production code in un-optimized build - which makes the tests incomplete, and gas tests unusable.",
